{"word":"G4784 - συγκατατίθεμαι - synkatatíthemai - soong-kat-at-ith'-em-ahee - Consent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγκατατίθεμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synkatatíthemai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soong-kat-at-ith'-em-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Consent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"விைைனச்சொல் - சம்மதி"},{"paragraph":"to deposit together with another"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2698 - κατατίθημι - katatíthēmi - kat-at-ith'-ay-mee/2698\">G2698</a>; to <i>deposit</i> (one&rsquo;s vote or opinion) in company <i>with</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>accord</i> with: - consent.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}